{"type": "article", "id": 26276, "title": "喜欢蓝染，可以关注The Hill-Side 和 Buaisou 合作系列", "description": "这系列包括手工染色的织边条纹布衬衫、围巾和领带。", "date": "2016-05-01T06:58:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7968, "name": "Coolhunting"}, {"id": 27036, "name": "绞染"}, {"id": 660, "name": "手工"}], "category": 17, "column": 24, "author": 18, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 175, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172837t3wJeXHcr8PCoZTi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p align=\"left\" class=\"\"><b><i><a href=\"http://www.coolhunting.com/style/the-hill-side-buaisou-2016-collaboration\">本文</a>由 Coolhunting 授权《好奇心日报》发布，即使我们允许了也不许转载。</i></b><br></p>\n<p align=\"left\">Coolhunting 最喜欢的两家布鲁克林品牌 <a href=\"http://coolhunting.com/tag/The%20Hill-Side\">The Hill-Side</a> 和 <a href=\"http://coolhunting.com/design/studio-visit-buaisou-brooklyn-japanese-sukumo-indigo-dyeing\">Buaisou</a> 合作推出了一个限量版的织边条纹布服装配饰系列——全部采用日本传统的绞染技术、以天然靛蓝染料手工染色。衬衫、方巾、领带和围巾都在日本德岛（Tokushima）生产，由 Buaisou 专业级的农民染色师打造——这一系列的款式简洁，美感也一目了然。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172832tOs9IhCmyAjrdRx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021728339vnEsa1wMC4UDTyk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p align=\"left\">说到工艺，绞染（shibori）是种触摸式防染染色技术。染色师把面料折叠、扭转、绑到特定物件上，浸染时产生各种图案纹样。值得注意的是，这一系列采用的是 100 % 全天然植物染料——由 Buaisou 的工艺师们以传统方式种植、收割和加工而成。最终成品是充满活力的“日本蓝”，颜色既纯正又深邃。全棉的条纹布料也源自日本。面料经染色后被运至纽约，在那里制成衬衫和配饰。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172833wEVABkhKNDPqytjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38653637\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021728344aq9RpLivMIxtVZb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39978214\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172834veqSlrEfGP5hTdw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43380615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172834jgLVKmh8bMSkein3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35902637\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172835U58InbLx6YJOidDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37408568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172835nOaV4WNY8gX76R1w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36757301\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172836xXiEA1pGnBFOS7TK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3563778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172836ATsV261mPREWajz3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37849018\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172837P7t64ICXDAn3akfl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3655244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>在线浏览整个 <a href=\"http://shop.thehill-side.com/search?q=Buaisou\">The Hill-Side + Buaisou</a> 系列。<i></i></p>\n<p>图片版权 The Hill-Side</p>\n<p>翻译 Alicia Lee</p>\n\n"}